<sect2 id="using-setup-shortcuts">
    <title
>配置快捷键</title>

    <para
>&digikam; 包含了 &kde; 通用快捷键设置，可通过<menuchoice
><guimenu
>设置</guimenu
><guimenuitem
>快捷键设置</guimenuitem
></menuchoice
>菜单项来配置。更多设置选项参考<ulink url="help:/fundamentals/kbd.html"
> &kde; 应用程序快捷键配置</ulink
> </para>
    <para
>&digikam; 默认快捷键： </para>

    <sect3 id="assign-rating">
        <title
>评星操作</title>

        <informaltable
><tgroup cols="2">
                <thead>
                    <row>
                        <entry
>评分</entry>
                        <entry
>快捷键</entry>
                    </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <row>
                        <entry
>未评星</entry>
                        <entry
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Ctrl;<keycap
>0</keycap
></keycombo
></entry>
                    </row>
                    <row>
                        <entry
>1 星</entry>
                        <entry
><keycombo action="simul"
>&Ctrl;<keycap
>1</keycap
